comment.narrative:
29-04-2021: 1. the Coordinating Ministry for Economic Affairs, Deputy Coordinator for the Food and Agribusiness Sector, allocated Special Formula NPK Fertilizers for Subsidized Cocoa in the 2020 budget year in 6 districts in South Sulawesi Province (Pinrang, Luwu, East Luwu, North Luwu), and 2 districts in Central Sulawesi Province (Poso and Parigi Moutong);
2. The Jembrana local government has allocated a budget through the agriculture office for the Kakao Lestari program of IDR 50,000,000 for clone mapping activities and IDR 70,000,000 to support the formation of PERDA, and has provided additional funds and budgets for the office of agriculture.
3. PT. PGE Ulubelu has expressed commitment to support the restoration of the batutegi catchment area in Ulu Belu District, Tanggamus Regency.
